en:
[b][u]Barriers:[/u][/b]
Exist in two variants - basic and sturdy.
Basic one can't be broken, sturdy breaks after {barrier_sturdy_health} hits.

Barriers don't count towards level completion.

[b][u]Blocks:[/u][/b]
Exist in two variants - basic and sturdy.
Basic blocks break after {block_health} hit, sturdy ones after {block_sturdy_health}.

Destroy all to complete a level.

[b][u]Score:[/u][/b]
Increases by 1 for every {multiplier_combo_step} destroyed elements, up to x{multiplier_max_combo}.
Grabbing difficulty increasing pickups (small/fast ball, smaller paddle) also increases multiplier independent of combo.
Max score multiplier: x{multiplier_max}.

ja: 続けるには{game_play}ボタンを押す

en: Press key to assign to action.

ja: メインメニューに戻りますか？

en: Basic paddle. Easy to use, easy to master.
Paddle with arms for additional bounce options.
Curved paddle. Rounded edges allow for more varied and unpredictable bounces.
It’s roguelike! Well, almost…\nTime moves (normally) when paddle moves, otherwise it slows down to a crawl.
Perfect choice for anyone who craves complete control over the ball.\nBounce angle depends on which part of the paddle is hit, with center sending the ball straight up.
